FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://api.library.local/v1

# Library Management API

API for managing a library (Books, Authors, Borrowers)

# Group Books

## Book Collection [/books]

### List All Books [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 101,
                "title": "The Lord of the Rings",
                "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
                "publishedYear": 1954
            }
        ]

### Add a New Book [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "title": "The Lord of the Rings",
            "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
            "publishedYear": 1954
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 102,
            "title": "The Lord of the Rings",
            "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
            "publishedYear": 1954
        }

## Book Resource [/books/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 101 (number, required) - Book ID

### Get a Book by ID [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 101,
            "title": "The Lord of the Rings",
            "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
            "publishedYear": 1954
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
            "error": "Book not found"
        }
